Mylan - Wikipedia





















 






Mylan

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Mylan





Trading name

Mylan N.V.



Formerly called

Milan



Type

Public (under Dutch law)


Traded as
NASDAQ: MYL
TASE: MYL
